{"tid":1065454,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"崇日毒撚：韓國音樂後勁不足，不出幾年會被日本音樂娛樂重新取代","createTime":"2019-03-17T09:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T05:39:36.000Z","uid":109923,"like":81,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"9847796d263f1b428c8056cca178a5ac541739d1","tid":1065454,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T09:18:54.000Z","msg":"以個人預測這一波韓國浪潮大概撐不到幾年就走下坡了，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為日本就算這幾年比較沒落、但基礎打的深又好，還是有機會再度把亞洲音樂娛樂這一塊版圖給拿回來</span>，韓國利用的是包裝還有訓練的力量，在音樂上還是略顯不足，我不看好韓國的原因就是這樣，其實對韓國人我不喜歡也不討厭。<br />\n <br />\n如果韓國人想要趁著熱潮多推出一些團體也大無不可啦，只不過這些團體不像樂團的壽命那麼長，就像只活過夏天的蟬，季節過完就死光光了，還是靠著本錢去應對比較好。"},{"pid":"75f66ce0560c0857b87a3a44f1cb0377ad249638","tid":1065454,"uid":109923,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T09:20:30.000Z","msg":"原文網址 <a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/home/creationDetail.php?sn=728720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fhome%2FcreationDetail.php%3Fsn%3D728720&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2FwzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=b1cb5128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/home/creationDetail.php?sn=728720</a><br />\n<br />\n發表時間：<span style=\"color: red;\">2010</span>-09-16 18:31"},{"pid":"ac83e5a48f2ed59b57e09a122a506d1e7b17d15a","tid":1065454,"uid":109923,"like":179,"dislike":11,"score":168,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T09:22:02.000Z","msg":"9年過去了<br />\n<br />\n韓國嘢越黎越hit，日本嘢越黎越頹，連AKB啲人都走去韓國女團<br />\n<br />\n然而，崇日毒撚繼續活係自己世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdc5ae09ab47efc2511bb5ed55f505b78d01120","tid":1065454,"uid":55874,"like":50,"dislike":5,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"韓團就係<br />\n韓國歌手就唔係 有實力嘅要幾多有幾多 成個產業好成熟<br />\nKoop is just a part of K music"},{"pid":"925bb1abc329d4d3ce3f83ce9a50ecf5c1611013","tid":1065454,"uid":109923,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T